Looking at the diff carefully, the schema changes are:

1. **`group`** gains a `type` field (`"control-plane"` / `"worker"`)
2. **`generics`** is eliminated — its fields (`script`, `ssh-public-key`, `user`, `control-plane-endpoint`, `machine-type`, `boot-disk-image`) move into specs (all optional per-spec entry)
